So what's a takeaway?

00:04:53.930 --> 00:04:57.930
Disloyalty causes Jehovah so much pain.

00:04:57.930 --> 00:05:00.930
But the opposite is also true.

00:05:00.930 --> 00:05:02.930
When we imitate Jehovah's loyal love,

00:05:02.930 --> 00:05:05.930
he must be so pleased.

00:05:05.930 --> 00:05:09.930
So when we do our best to maintain a loving atmosphere in our marriage,

00:05:09.930 --> 00:05:11.930
even though it isn't easy,

00:05:11.930 --> 00:05:13.930
or if we feel mistreated,

00:05:13.930 --> 00:05:15.930
when we are loyal to our brothers and sisters

00:05:15.930 --> 00:05:18.930
and work to restore a damaged relationship,

00:05:18.930 --> 00:05:20.930
even when they hurt us,

00:05:20.930 --> 00:05:23.930
we make Jehovah happy.

00:05:23.930 --> 00:05:25.930
Yeah, we're imitating him.

00:05:25.930 --> 00:05:27.930
It's not mechanical.

00:05:27.930 --> 00:05:29.930
It's an act of loyal love.

00:05:29.930 --> 00:05:31.930
We don't just forgive.

00:05:31.930 --> 00:05:33.930
We love.

00:05:33.930 --> 00:05:35.930
Another takeaway.

00:05:35.930 --> 00:05:38.930
